title: Bug 132103: No objects under Context in palette when scripting a data set
OB: When scripting a data set, there are no objects displayed under the Context section in the palette.
EB: Expected behavior: The Context section in the palette should show objects that can be used when scripting a data set. In particular, the object 'BeforeOpen' should be available.
SR: To resolve this issue, investigate why the objects under the Context section are not being displayed when scripting a data set. Ensure that the 'BeforeOpen' object is included in the list of objects available in the Context section.
